abstract_str: heath hall in hampstead , north london was originally put on the market three years ago for # 100 million . the 24,000 sq/ft trophy home on the bishops avenue in north london is set in a plot of around __2.5-acres__ . bought as a wreck for # 5million in 2006 , developer andreas __panayiotou__ spent millions on the renovation . the asking price was dropped to # 65million in 2012 but the property still failed to sell .
